### Input configuration
# Get input names: swaymsg -t get_inputs
# Read `man 5 sway-input`

# Example touchpad:
#   input "2:14:SynPS/2_Synaptics_TouchPad" {
#       dwt enabled
#       tap enabled
#       natural_scroll enabled
#       middle_emulation enabled
#   }

# Example keyboard:
#   input "type:keyboard" {
#       xkb_layout us,bg
#       xkb_options grp:alt_shift_toggle
#   }
